description:
Lauren Slater buys what she thinks is a farm in New Hampshire but soon discovers it was once a landfill. &nbsp;
Ivan Kuraev is 8 when he falls deeply in love with a classmate.&nbsp; &nbsp;
Ivan Kuraev &rsquo;s doting Russian grandmother gets revenge on his boyhood enemies. &nbsp;
Charles Pugh &rsquo;s grandmother is the most loving and supportive person in his life until she gets Alzheimer's disease. NOTE: When offensive or FCC-prohibited words appear, they are bleeped and listed in the Content Advisory. &nbsp;Sensitive content will be given an on-air caution and will be noted here in the description.
